: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>、有气度。一定不能找小家子气的男人，即使他爱你。因为一点点小事就吃醋，不论你是因公与上司出去应酬，还是因私与多年不见的朋友聚会，在你回家后大吵大闹或者阴沉着脸半天不搭理你的男人，其实是自私的。爱一个人也要给她自由。作为现在这个社会的女性，要有自己的社交圈子，要独立、自主。不能给你自由空间的男人千万不能要。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>、身体健康。不要求那个男的有多么的高大威猛，但一定要身体健健康康的。一个女人身体有点毛病可以称之为弱不禁风，如果一个男人整天病怏怏的，你说像啥话。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>、不当乖宝宝。凡事都征求妈妈看法，毫无自己主见，嘴巴里动不动就说：<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>妈妈说<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>妈妈说<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;</span>这样的乖宝宝坚决不能要。记住，你嫁的是一个男人，并不是那个男人的妈妈。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>、有一份稳定的收入。所谓贫贱夫妻百事哀，如果一个男人连孩子的奶粉钱都拿不出来，这个月初就开始担心下个月的供房款，那么，你跟着他只有吃苦的份了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span>、自信。浑身散发着自信味道的男人，能让女人放心地依靠。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>、外貌匹配。不要求他一定英俊潇洒，但他要看上去不至于引起<span lang=\"EN-US\">&ldquo;</span>公愤<span lang=\"EN-US\">&rdquo;</span>。总不能你亭亭玉立一大美女，身边跟随一矮个的黑胖子吧<span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>、细心又有情趣。他可以不记得你大伯小叔三姑四姨的生日，但你的生日与结婚纪念日一定要记住，这两个日子在婚姻生活中是很重要的。能够出去浪漫一下还有礼物收，那是最好的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>、无不良嗜好。烟可以抽一点，酒可以喝一点，但不能太过。你总不想天天回去面对一个醉醺醺的酒鬼，嘴里还不时散发着一股浓浓烟臭味的人吧。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 11</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">、社交能力强。一起出去应酬，他只知道站在一旁傻笑而找不到话题与你的朋友交谈，凡事需要你出来撑场面的男人，会让你脸面无光。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>、大男人气概。你在外面受到欺负时，他能够挺身而出，毫不犹豫地为你出头，真真切切地保护你。这样的大男人就值得你考虑托付终身。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span>、有责任心。男人一定要有责任心，自己做的事要敢于自己承担，无论是公事还是私事。那种一有事就往别人身上推的男人，不但卑鄙而且可耻。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\"> <br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">　　<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>、平和。如果一个男人不能以一颗平和的心去看待自己的得失，整天愤世嫉俗，怪社会不公，怨生活不平，那么你和他在一起也会影响你的心态，给你的心理造成巨大的压力，导致你不快乐地生活</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; color: #003300; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><strong><font color=\"#333333\">关键词:</font></strong></span><span style=\"color: #333333\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><a href=\"http://www.vangophoto.com/show.php\"><strong><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">深圳时尚婚纱</font></strong></a><strong>&nbsp; </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><a href=\"http://www.vangophoto.com/news.php?id=44\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><strong><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">深圳婚纱摄影工作室</font></strong></span></a></span><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><span><strong>&nbsp;<font color=\"#556c88\">&nbsp;</font></strong></span></span><strong><a href=\"http://www.vangophoto.com/news.php?id=43\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">深圳商业广告摄影</font></span></a><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><a href=\"http://www.vangophoto.com/news.php?id=42\"><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">深圳个性写真</font></a>&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><a href=\"http://www.vangophoto.com/news.php?id=41\"><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">深圳80后个性婚</font></a><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">&nbsp; </font></span><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><a href=\"http://www.vangophoto.com/price.php\"><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">深圳时尚婚纱摄影</font></a><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></span><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><a href=\"http://www.vangophoto.com/news.php?id=39\"><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">深圳婚纱照团购</font></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><strong><a href=\"http://www.vangophoto.com/news.php?id=37\"><font color=\"#4c4c4c\">深圳婚纱照哪里好</font></a> </strong></span></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><strong>梵谷视觉感谢您的关注</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: x-small\"><span><strong>转载本文请说明出处</strong></span></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</span